 activation. The protein encoded by this gene has nine SCRs with the first two
 repeats having heparin binding properties, a region within repeats 5-7 having
 heparin binding and C reactive protein binding properties, and the C-terminal
 repeats being similar to a complement component 3 b (C3b) binding domain.
